dct_description_sm: Map 1: Woodbury Creek from Red Highway drawbridge to Woodbury.

Map shows Woodbury Creek along with a Red Highway Drawbridge, West Jersey and Seashore Rail Road. Shows a dredged location along the creek and also includes a locality map and diagrams of the Red Drawbridge, the West Jersey and Seashore Railroad fixed bridge, and a plan for the fixed highway bridge at Broad Street.
Map 2: Woodbury Creek from Delaware River to Red Highway Drawbridge.
Map shows soundings of Woodbury Creek, proposed cutoffs, the Red Highway drawbridge, and the white highway drawbridge. Includes a diagram of the white highway drawbridge.
